{"type": "article", "id": 13767, "title": "搞怪灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-20T07:45:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021257396MoRVBYE9lDKafe5.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t德国设计师 Ingo Maurer 从上个世纪 60 年代开始就致力于奇思妙想的灯具和照明设计，今年他推出了四款有趣的灯具，其中，“what we do counts’” 看上去像是一个大大的平面漫画，而 “i ricchi poveri – monument for a bulb” 的灯座上有许多小人，像在为灯泡立碑，“lucellino” 像是一个飞翔的鸟，而 “walking bulb” 的 LED 灯则不停地进行着水平的 360 度翻转，似乎是在向前走一样。<a href=\"http://www.ingo-maurer.com/de/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414504tQ8C1MPBNHasco2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141451SlZOteEvUhosPTbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74105263\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141451dUpEGO8HWgNBmS1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141451T8qYV2r9zUIZ5AEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141452mYQkEw6uxjgoS7Mh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141452QXaNAFDKfsSbH8k4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78728606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141453VSGbJvqP6XTuihRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141453draEWtY14MFwTxH5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73105134\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141454YvmiBpLeHJzfxCE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141454Wjz3ubH8IE0kqZXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10268949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}